data.description: Nice three bedroom home on a quiet low traffic street in the Passyunk Square area of South Philadelphia. This is an excellent opportunity to live in this desirable area at an affordable price. 1st floor has an enclosed entryway with beveled glass door to the living room. Large front windows offer plenty of light looking out to a tree lined street.  Dinning area, Kitchen with upper and lower wood cabinets and out to a nice size rear yard. 2nd floor has three bedrooms and modern 3 piece bathroom.  Basement level has a laundry area and is clean cement.  The home has been freshly painted and is ready for furniture.
